definitions: (of an electronic device) making a short high-pitched sound or sounds

examples.text: a bleeping red display on the exercise machine

shortDefinitions: making short high-pitched sound or sounds

definitions: used to express exasperation or annoyance, in place of an expletive

examples.text: we didn't do a bleeping thing, and we're still getting hung

shortDefinitions: used to express exasperation or annoyance
